                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature hit by the mezlan's ooze globule takes a -15-foot circumstance penalty to all Speeds for 1 minute. On a critical hit, a target standing on a solid surface also becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Immobilized]{Immobilized}, while a target Flying via wings falls to the ground and becomes unable to Fly.</p>\n<p>A target can end all effects by @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Escape]{Escaping} (DC 32) or spending a total of 3 @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Interact]{Interact} actions to free itself.</p>"
